---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Bilingual from '../../components/Bilingual.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Camera & Projection · CS Notebook">
  <article class="space-y-6">
    <header>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-cyan mb-2">Graphics / Camera & Projection</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">
        <Bilingual><span slot="zh">相机与投影</span><span slot="en">Camera & Projection</span></Bilingual>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">相机决定了<b>看到什么</b>，投影决定了<b>怎么看到</b>。3D 渲染中相机由三要素定义：<b>位置</b>、<b>朝向</b>（look 方向 + up 向量）、<b>视锥</b>（FOV + 近远裁剪面）。下方演示可拖动 FOV 滑块观察透视视锥的变化，并对比透视 vs 正交投影。</span>
          <span slot="en">The camera determines <b>what is seen</b>; projection determines <b>how it is seen</b>. A 3D camera is defined by three things: <b>position</b>, <b>orientation</b> (look direction + up vector), and the <b>view frustum</b> (FOV + near/far planes). Drag the FOV slider below to watch the perspective frustum change, and compare perspective vs orthographic.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="glass p-5">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mb-4">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">
          <span>FOV</span>
          <input id="cam-fov" type="range" min="20" max="120" value="60" class="w-48" />
          <span id="cam-fov-val" class="font-mono text-primary-cyan w-12">60°</span>
        </label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">
          <select id="cam-mode" class="btn !py-1.5"></select>
        </label>
      </div>
      <svg id="cam-svg" viewBox="0 0 600 320" class="w-full viz-stage"></svg>
      <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mt-2">
        <Bilingual><span slot="zh">黄色视锥示意相机视野；近裁剪面（绿）与远裁剪面（红）之间为可见区域。物体在视锥外会被<b>视锥剔除</b>。</span><span slot="en">Yellow frustum marks the camera's view; between the near plane (green) and far plane (red) is the visible volume. Anything outside is <b>frustum-culled</b>.</span></Bilingual>
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">透视 vs 正交投影</span><span slot="en">Perspective vs Orthographic</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="text-ink-muted text-left"><tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">维度</span><span slot="en">Aspect</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4 text-primary-cyan"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">透视投影</span><span slot="en">Perspective</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4 text-primary-purple"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">正交投影</span><span slot="en">Orthographic</span></Bilingual></th></tr></thead>
          <tbody class="text-ink">
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">近大远小</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">✓ 有</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red">✗ 无</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">平行线</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">相交于灭点</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">保持平行</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">w 分量</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">w = -z（与深度相关）</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">w = 1（恒为 1）</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">适用场景</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">3D 游戏、第一人称</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">2D UI、CAD、等距游戏</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">代表游戏</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">大多数 3A 3D 游戏</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">暗黑破坏神、星露谷</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">视锥与裁剪面</span><span slot="en">View Frustum & Clipping Planes</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">视锥是相机的可见空间——一个被 6 个平面截断的金字塔：<b>近裁剪面</b>、<b>远裁剪面</b>、上、下、左、右。物体必须在视锥内才会被渲染。近裁剪面太近会导致<b>深度冲突</b>（Z-fighting）——两个相近表面的深度值因精度不足而闪烁。远裁剪面太远会浪费填充率，但能避免远处物体突然弹出。平衡近远比是关键——通常近面 0.1、远面 1000。</span>
          <span slot="en">The frustum is the camera's visible volume — a pyramid truncated by 6 planes: <b>near</b>, <b>far</b>, top, bottom, left, right. Only objects inside are rendered. A too-near near plane causes <b>Z-fighting</b> — two close surfaces flicker due to insufficient depth precision. A too-far far plane wastes fill rate but avoids distant objects popping in. Balancing the near/far ratio is key — typically near 0.1, far 1000.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
      <pre class="bg-[color:var(--code-bg)] rounded-lg p-4 mt-3 overflow-x-auto text-sm"><code>// 透视投影矩阵（OpenGL 风格）
// fovy: 垂直 FOV, aspect: 宽/高, n: 近, f: 远
mat4 perspective(float fovy, float aspect, float n, float f) &#123;
    float t = 1.0 / tan(fovy / 2.0);
    return mat4(
        t / aspect, 0,  0,                  0,
        0,         t,  0,                  0,
        0,         0,  -(f+n)/(f-n),       -2*f*n/(f-n),
        0,         0,  -1,                  0
    );
&#125;
// 经透视除法后 z 范围 [-1, 1]（NDC），非线性分布——近处精度高，远处精度低</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">视锥剔除</span><span slot="en">Frustum Culling</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">把整个场景每个物体逐顶点测试是否在视锥内代价过高。优化做法：用每个物体的<b>包围球</b>（Bounding Sphere）或<b>AABB</b>（Axis-Aligned Bounding Box）做粗筛——只需检测包围体与 6 个视锥平面的关系。若包围体完全在某平面外侧，物体被剔除；若完全在内部，所有顶点直接通过；若部分相交，则保留并交给后续逐顶点裁剪。游戏引擎中常见的<b>层次包围体</b>（BVH）进一步加速这一过程。</span>
          <span slot="en">Testing every vertex of every object against the frustum is too costly. The optimization: use each object's <b>bounding sphere</b> or <b>AABB</b> (Axis-Aligned Bounding Box) for a coarse test — check the bounding volume against the 6 frustum planes. If fully outside any plane, the object is culled; if fully inside, all vertices pass; if partially intersecting, keep it for per-vertex clipping. Engines typically accelerate this with a <b>BVH</b> (Bounding Volume Hierarchy).</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">延伸阅读</span><span slot="en">Further Reading</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <ul class="text-sm text-ink-muted space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
        <li><Bilingual><span slot="zh"><a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/topics/coord-transform">坐标变换</a>：投影矩阵 P 在 MVP 链中的作用。</span><span slot="en"><a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/topics/coord-transform">Coords & Transforms</a>: the role of the P matrix in the MVP chain.</span></Bilingual></li>
        <li><Bilingual><span slot="zh"><a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/topics/render-paths">渲染路径</a>：相机视野如何被光栅化与着色。</span><span slot="en"><a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/topics/render-paths">Render Paths</a>: how the camera's view is rasterized and shaded.</span></Bilingual></li>
        <li><Bilingual><span slot="zh"><a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/graphics/render">3D 渲染管线可视化页</a>：可拖拽 WebGL 演示相机视角。</span><span slot="en"><a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/graphics/render">3D Render Pipeline visualizer</a>: draggable WebGL demo with camera view.</span></Bilingual></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const SVGNS = 'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg';
  const svg = document.getElementById('cam-svg') as unknown as SVGSVGElement;
  const fovInput = document.getElementById('cam-fov') as HTMLInputElement;
  const fovVal = document.getElementById('cam-fov-val');
  const modeSel = document.getElementById('cam-mode') as HTMLSelectElement;

  const CAM_X = 540, CAM_Y = 160;
  const NEAR_DIST = 80;
  const FAR_DIST = 480;

  function lang(): 'zh' | 'en' {
    return document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-lang') === 'en' ? 'en' : 'zh';
  }

  function fovToHalfHeight(fovDeg: number, dist: number, isPerspective: boolean): number {
    if (!isPerspective) return 90;
    const rad = (fovDeg * Math.PI) / 180;
    return Math.tan(rad / 2) * dist;
  }

  function render() {
    const fov = Number(fovInput.value);
    const isPersp = modeSel.value === 'perspective';
    if (fovVal) fovVal.textContent = `${fov}°`;

    svg.innerHTML = '';

    const bg = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'rect');
    bg.setAttribute('x', '0'); bg.setAttribute('y', '0');
    bg.setAttribute('width', '600'); bg.setAttribute('height', '320');
    bg.setAttribute('fill', 'rgba(15,23,42,0.4)');
    svg.appendChild(bg);

    const nearH = fovToHalfHeight(fov, NEAR_DIST, isPersp);
    const farH = isPersp ? fovToHalfHeight(fov, FAR_DIST, isPersp) : nearH;

    const nearLeftX = CAM_X - NEAR_DIST;
    const farLeftX = CAM_X - FAR_DIST;
    const nearTopY = CAM_Y - nearH, nearBotY = CAM_Y + nearH;
    const farTopY = CAM_Y - farH, farBotY = CAM_Y + farH;

    const frustum = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'polygon');
    frustum.setAttribute('points', `${nearLeftX},${nearTopY} ${farLeftX},${farTopY} ${farLeftX},${farBotY} ${nearLeftX},${nearBotY}`);
    frustum.setAttribute('fill', 'rgba(251,191,36,0.12)');
    frustum.setAttribute('stroke', '#FBBF24');
    frustum.setAttribute('stroke-width', '1.5');
    svg.appendChild(frustum);

    const viewLine = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'line');
    viewLine.setAttribute('x1', String(CAM_X)); viewLine.setAttribute('y1', String(CAM_Y));
    viewLine.setAttribute('x2', String(farLeftX)); viewLine.setAttribute('y2', String(CAM_Y));
    viewLine.setAttribute('stroke', '#94A3B8');
    viewLine.setAttribute('stroke-width', '1');
    viewLine.setAttribute('stroke-dasharray', '3 3');
    svg.appendChild(viewLine);

    const near = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'line');
    near.setAttribute('x1', String(nearLeftX)); near.setAttribute('y1', String(nearTopY));
    near.setAttribute('x2', String(nearLeftX)); near.setAttribute('y2', String(nearBotY));
    near.setAttribute('stroke', '#22C55E');
    near.setAttribute('stroke-width', '3');
    svg.appendChild(near);

    const far = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'line');
    far.setAttribute('x1', String(farLeftX)); far.setAttribute('y1', String(farTopY));
    far.setAttribute('x2', String(farLeftX)); far.setAttribute('y2', String(farBotY));
    far.setAttribute('stroke', '#EF4444');
    far.setAttribute('stroke-width', '3');
    svg.appendChild(far);

    [[nearTopY, farTopY], [nearBotY, farBotY]].forEach(([y1, y2]) => {
      const l = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'line');
      l.setAttribute('x1', String(nearLeftX)); l.setAttribute('y1', String(y1));
      l.setAttribute('x2', String(farLeftX)); l.setAttribute('y2', String(y2));
      l.setAttribute('stroke', '#FBBF24');
      l.setAttribute('stroke-width', '1');
      svg.appendChild(l);
    });

    const camIcon = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'circle');
    camIcon.setAttribute('cx', String(CAM_X)); camIcon.setAttribute('cy', String(CAM_Y));
    camIcon.setAttribute('r', '6');
    camIcon.setAttribute('fill', '#22D3EE');
    camIcon.setAttribute('stroke', '#fff');
    camIcon.setAttribute('stroke-width', '2');
    svg.appendChild(camIcon);

    const labels = [
      { x: CAM_X + 8, y: CAM_Y - 10, t: lang() === 'en' ? 'Camera' : '相机', fill: '#22D3EE', anchor: '' },
      { x: nearLeftX, y: nearTopY - 8, t: lang() === 'en' ? 'Near' : '近裁剪面', fill: '#22C55E', anchor: 'middle' },
      { x: farLeftX, y: farTopY - 8, t: lang() === 'en' ? 'Far' : '远裁剪面', fill: '#EF4444', anchor: 'middle' },
    ];
    labels.forEach((l) => {
      const txt = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'text');
      txt.setAttribute('x', String(l.x)); txt.setAttribute('y', String(l.y));
      txt.setAttribute('fill', l.fill);
      txt.setAttribute('font-size', '12');
      txt.setAttribute('font-weight', '600');
      if (l.anchor) txt.setAttribute('text-anchor', l.anchor);
      txt.textContent = l.t;
      svg.appendChild(txt);
    });

    const obj = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'rect');
    const objX = CAM_X - 280;
    obj.setAttribute('x', String(objX - 12));
    obj.setAttribute('y', String(CAM_Y - 25));
    obj.setAttribute('width', '24'); obj.setAttribute('height', '50');
    obj.setAttribute('fill', '#A78BFA');
    obj.setAttribute('opacity', '0.7');
    svg.appendChild(obj);
    const objLabel = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'text');
    objLabel.setAttribute('x', String(objX));
    objLabel.setAttribute('y', String(CAM_Y + 50));
    objLabel.setAttribute('fill', '#A78BFA');
    objLabel.setAttribute('font-size', '11');
    objLabel.setAttribute('text-anchor', 'middle');
    objLabel.textContent = lang() === 'en' ? 'Object' : '物体';
    svg.appendChild(objLabel);

    const culled = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'rect');
    culled.setAttribute('x', String(CAM_X - 480 - 12));
    culled.setAttribute('y', String(CAM_Y - 100));
    culled.setAttribute('width', '24'); culled.setAttribute('height', '24');
    culled.setAttribute('fill', 'rgba(239,68,68,0.3)');
    culled.setAttribute('stroke', '#EF4444');
    culled.setAttribute('stroke-dasharray', '3 2');
    svg.appendChild(culled);
    const culledLabel = document.createElementNS(SVGNS, 'text');
    culledLabel.setAttribute('x', String(CAM_X - 480));
    culledLabel.setAttribute('y', String(CAM_Y - 108));
    culledLabel.setAttribute('fill', '#EF4444');
    culledLabel.setAttribute('font-size', '11');
    culledLabel.setAttribute('text-anchor', 'middle');
    culledLabel.textContent = lang() === 'en' ? 'Culled' : '已剔除';
    svg.appendChild(culledLabel);
  }

  fovInput.addEventListener('input', render);
  modeSel.addEventListener('change', render);
  document.addEventListener('langchange', render);

  // 填充投影模式下拉
  function fillModeOptions() {
    const en = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-lang') === 'en';
    const opts: [string, string, string][] = [
      ['perspective', en ? 'Perspective' : '透视', en ? 'Perspective' : '透视'],
      ['orthographic', en ? 'Orthographic' : '正交', en ? 'Orthographic' : '正交'],
    ];
    modeSel.innerHTML = '';
    const cur = modeSel.value || 'perspective';
    opts.forEach(([v, label]) => {
      const o = document.createElement('option');
      o.value = v; o.textContent = label;
      modeSel.appendChild(o);
    });
    modeSel.value = cur;
  }
  fillModeOptions();
  document.addEventListener('langchange', fillModeOptions);
  render();
</script>
